snippet.title: Oriental Magnetic Yellow (OMY) - Good Pierrot [1995]
snippet.description:
See also:
Beyond the Muscle - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RmisimxEDcw

A parody band of Yellow Magic Orchestra, formed by VGM composers. The members were: Shinji Hosoe, Nobuyoshi Sano, Takayuki Aihara and Hiroto Sasaki.
